{"tid":2253520,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"滙豐銅獅子重現吸引市民拍照　小股東冀「恢復威武」","createTime":"2020-10-22T08:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T08:38:32.000Z","uid":241764,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"76dc652267996e1fc7f00606cb92fc921d86c36e","tid":2253520,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:00:53.000Z","msg":"(節錄)<br />\n早在20多年前曾與銅獅子合照的陳先生說，得知銅獅子早前被破壞感到心痛，開心一對獅子已修復。他認為，銅獅子代表滙豐銀行，銅獅子被修復，相信銀行前景亦會好起來。<br />\n<br />\n本身是滙豐客戶和小股東的黎小姐說，銅獅子代表香港人的獅子山下精神，雖然滙豐在派息問題令小股民失望，但她仍希望重新展示的獅子能早日「恢復威武」，香港能再次出發。<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556112-20201022.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556112-20201022.htm&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPaCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=88db5828\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556112-20201022.htm&h=541cea04\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556112-20201022.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n陳先生說，得知銅獅子早前被破壞感到心痛，如今已修復得感到開心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1556112_1_L_20201022151153.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1556112_1_L_20201022151153.jpg&h=282c9289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為隻獅子心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c33f9d285308e4993777c26d4908216eed161741","tid":2253520,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:20:41.000Z","msg":"係咪$80 5仔既股東"},{"pid":"c69d5f7db77728f196bf26a2841bd45c265768b7","tid":2253520,"uid":9116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T08:22:42.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">本身是滙豐客戶和小股東的黎小姐</span>說，銅獅子代表香港人的獅子山下精神，雖然滙豐在派息問題令小股民失望，但她仍希望重新展示的獅子能早日「恢復威武」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.co